Makro has provided the first details on its Black Friday 2018 sale, set to launch soon. Makro’s “Black 5 Day” sale is coming soon, the company stated on its website – hinting at five days of specials over Black Friday and Cyber Monday. “Major savings! Get ready for Black Friday and Cyber Monday deals,” said Makro. Makro added that there will be: Users can register for updates on the sale on the Makro site. Black Friday is set to take place on 23 November 2018.